<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="15Apr1925"><font color="red">15 April 1925</font> <i>BLHW</i> (to Harriet Weaver): I am leaving for the clinique &lsquo;for a few days&rsquo;. I shall send you a telegram from there. Enclosed is the piece for Mr Eliot which I sent off with the combined momentum of self, 4 magnifying glasses, Mr Morel and my son. And now &mdash; a <i>fiat lux!</i> </div>
